      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-fuchsia-50 border-[3px] border-[#A855F7] p-6 md:p-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">MY EXPERIENCE</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>

        <div class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 font-black mb-8">
          The Human Touch That Cost <span class="text-[#A855F7]">$180/Year</span>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            A consultant needed a website for her new practice. Same offer, tested both platforms. She was excited about B12's "human designer review."
          </p>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#A855F7] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE MIXO TEST</h3>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Generated in:</strong> 47 seconds</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">First impression:</strong> Site looked professional</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">AI copy quality:</strong> Surprisingly good</p>
            <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-gray-900">Customization:</strong> Tweaked sections, adjusted colors</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#A855F7]">Total time to publish:</strong> 3 hours</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-[#A855F7] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">THE B12 TEST</h3>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Generated in:</strong> 90 seconds</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Then waited:</strong> 48 hours for human review</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Designer sent:</strong> Revisions with spacing tweaks</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">She requested:</strong> Additional changes</p>
            <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900">Another wait:</strong> 24 hours for second review</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-gray-900"><strong class="text-[#A855F7]">Total time to publish:</strong> 5 days</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-purple-100 border-l-[4px] border-[#A855F7] p-6 my-6">
            <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold mb-2">Mixo Site:</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 1,200 visitors</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 34 inquiry form submissions</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 2.83% conversion rate</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ Cost: $54 for 6 months</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold mb-2">B12 Site:</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 1,100 visitors</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 31 inquiry submissions</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ 2.82% conversion rate</p>
                <p>‚Ä¢ Cost: $180 for 6 months</p>
              </div>
            </div>
