        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#A855F7] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üéØ</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Premium Fields Benefit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Lawyers, financial advisors, consultants: the polished look converts high-ticket clients. The $180/year is negligible vs $5,000+ per client.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-6 hover:border-[#A855F7] transition-colors">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üìä</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Conversion Rates Identical</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">2.83% vs 2.82% difference is statistical noise. Human polish didn't move the needle on actual lead generation.</p>
        </div>

